AtBuss is an Android app for showing real time info about buses in Trondheim, Norway.

Android API version 7 (2.1) and up are supported.

To clone it:

1. Download Android Studio
2. Select "Check out from Version Control" -> GitHub
3. Select "Use default gradle wrapper (recommended)" -> OK

Dependencies are handled automatically, but are:
http://code.google.com/p/json-simple/
http://actionbarsherlock.com/
